business or working visas. the usual tourist single-entry visa is valid for a visit of 30 days and must be used within three months of the date of issue. a double-entry tourist visa must be used within six months of the date of issue. it is possible to secure a tourist visa for up to 90 days for citizens of some countries. tourist visa extensions can be applied for at the local entry & exit bureaus against handing in the following documents: valid passport, visa extension application form including one 2-inch-sized picture, a copy of the registration form of temporary 